	* Fixed bug #3154: Misspelling in instal tool

2006-04-06  Stanislas Rolland  <stanislas.rolland@fructifor.ca>

	* rtehtmlarea: fix bugtracker issue #3120: transforming text in link in Firefox may take excessive time.
